sentence: what are the major cities in states through which the mississippi runs ?
sentence-with-vars: what are the major cities in states through which the river0 runs ?
sql: select city.city_name from city where city.population > 150000 and city.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' mississippi ' and river.length > 750 ) ;
sql-with-vars: select city.city_name from city where city.population > 150000 and city.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' river0 ' and river.length > number0 ) ;
